headline: JBL Gains Traction in AI Infrastructure Space: Will This Fuel Revenue?
summary: JBL is betting big on AI data centers, expanding full-stack infrastructure and targeting $12.1B in AI-related revenue by fiscal 2026.

headline: Jabil Invests in EHT Semi to Accelerate Advanced RF and Pulsed Power Solutions for Next-Generation Semiconductor Manufacturing
summary: ST. PETERSBURG, Fla., January 20, 2026--Jabil Inc. (NYSE: JBL), a global leader in engineering, supply chain, and manufacturing solutions, announced today a strategic minority investment and manufacturing collaboration with Eagle Harbor Technologies, Inc. (dba, EHT Semi), a pioneer in RF and pulsed-power systems.
